<p>How do I use a parameter that consist a string in a where statement within a <code>with</code> clause which is bold in the codes. I tried doing that method but its doesn't work. </p>  <p>I have added a parameter called @param nvarchar(max) already.</p>  <pre><code>WITH Sales_CTE (SalesPersonID, SalesOrderID, SalesYear) AS (     SELECT SalesPersonID, SalesOrderID, YEAR(OrderDate) AS SalesYear     FROM Sales.SalesOrderHeader     **WHERE SalesPersonID IN ('+ @param +')** ) SELECT SalesPersonID, COUNT(SalesOrderID) AS TotalSales, SalesYear FROM Sales_CTE GROUP BY SalesYear, SalesPersonID </code></pre>